criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Aged >18 years old;

          -  Male or female patients;

          -  Patients undergoing elective standard diagnostic EGD;

          -  Negative polymerase chain reaction (PCR) test on nasopharyngeal swab 24 or 48 hours
             prior to the test;

          -  No anatomical deformity of nose and throat, no known diseases of nose and throat;

          -  Signed informed consent

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Females who are pregnant or lactating.
